    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Light sphere; Arcane Strike or Imbued Strike.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Whenever you successfully hit an enemy that is vulnerable to light (such as by the light blindness, light sensitivity, or sunlight powerlessness universal monster rules) with a melee weapon you have imbued with your Arcane Strike or Imbued Strike feat, you deal an additional 1d6 points of damage to the target of your attack. The struck creature must also succeed at a Fortitude saving throw (DC 10 + 1/2 your character level + your Strength modifier) or become staggered for 1 round. This bypasses the immunity to Fortitude saves usually granted by some creature types.</p>\n",
